# Performance Rules

## Laravel Performance
- Use Laravel's caching where appropriate
- Optimize database queries
- Use proper database indexing
- Implement query caching
- Use proper database relationships

## Vue Performance
- Use Vue's built-in performance features
- Implement proper code splitting
- Use lazy loading for components
- Optimize component rendering
- Use proper state management

## Asset Optimization
- Use proper asset bundling
- Implement proper asset caching
- Use proper image optimization
- Implement proper CSS/JS minification
- Use proper CDN configuration

## API Performance
- Implement proper API caching
- Use proper API pagination
- Optimize API responses
- Use proper API rate limiting
- Implement proper API monitoring

## General Performance
- Monitor application performance
- Use proper logging
- Implement proper error handling
- Use proper debugging tools
- Follow performance best practices
